f669407319fe6af212a131234","tid":86086,"uid":20222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T00:16:33.000Z","msg":"因為日本家用console 既佔有率高過pc 好多好多<br />\n所以先會忽略pc game 依個平台"}]}